    <note>Wu(3) Zhongfu [1967] Zeren's [1985] granduncle. Shenli [1980] had the same generational name and address as Zeli [4027] and his other sons. Zhongfu's father held office under the Southern Tang. His son Bingli's [4019] father-in-law, Chen(1) Gang [3070], was Chen(1) Kuo's [64] father. His son Keli [4016] was Di(1) Fei's [1633] grandson-in-law. XCB, 189.12b, 191.10b, 192.4a-4b, 295.5b; Hubei TZ, 123.25a; SS, 322.3b; Zeng Gong, WJ, 44.3a; Du Dagui, 'xia,' 15.15b. CBD, 2, 1142.</note>
